    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "Location": "",
    "cnWords": "Tommy，我昨晚去歌舞厅拍了些照片。中国花瓶和欧洲油画，它们还在歌舞厅里。你是怎么卖'空气'的？",
    "enWords": "Tommy, I took some photos at the dance hall last night. The Chinese vase and the European painting are still there. How did you sell 'air'?",
